00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:19.920
Om. Salutations to You, O Lord of the Ganas.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:26.400
You are the Manifestation of the Divine Principle

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:32.320
You alone are the Doer.

00:00:32.960 --> 00:00:38.320
You alone are the Supporter and the Sustainer.

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:44.080
You alone are the Remover and Destroyer.

00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:51.240
You are everything even indeed the Formless Spirit

00:00:51.720 --> 00:00:56.920
You are the Embodiment of the Soul eternally

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.360
I speak Divine Law.

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:01.840
I speak the Truth.

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:04.560
Protect thou me.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:07.400
Be propitious to the speaker

00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:10.360
and the listener.

00:01:10.480 --> 00:01:13.360
Watch over the one who gives

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:16.040
and the one who receives.

00:01:16.120 --> 00:01:19.120
Show favor to the learned scholar

00:01:19.240 --> 00:01:21.920
and to the pupil.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.760
Protect from behind.

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:27.840
Protect from the front.

00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:30.400
Protect from the left side.

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:33.680
Protect from the right side.

00:01:33.800 --> 00:01:36.520
Protect from above.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:39.400
Protect from below.

00:01:39.480 --> 00:01:44.680
From all directions guard and protect me constantly

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:47.000
You are the Spoken Word

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:49.240
You are the Spoken Word

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:52.040
Joy is Your essence.

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:54.720
Formless Spirit is youor nature

00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:59.080
You are Existence, Consciousness and Joy unequalled.

00:01:59.160 --> 00:02:02.960
You are the Supreme Spirit manifested.

00:02:03.080 --> 00:02:08.120
You are all Knowledge and Understanding.

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:12.680
This whole world is born from You.

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:17.280
This whole world is sustained by You.

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:22.480
This whole world will dissolve in You.

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:26.960
This whole world returns to You.

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:32.200
You are Earth, Water, Fire, Air and Ether

00:02:32.320 --> 00:02:36.200
You are the four parts of speech.

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:39.920
You are beyond the three attributes

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:43.560
You are beyond the three bodies.

00:02:43.640 --> 00:02:47.040
You are beyond the three times.

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:51.840
You are eternally stationed at Mooladhara Chakra.

00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:55.760
You are the Essence of the three Shaktis.

00:02:55.880 --> 00:03:00.120
On You Yogis meditate constantly.

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:03.800
You are Lord Brahma. You are Shri Vishnu.

00:03:03.880 --> 00:03:07.200
You are Lord Shiva. You are Shri Indra.

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:10.800
You are the God of Fire, You are Lord of the Wind.

00:03:10.880 --> 00:03:14.320
You are the Sun and You are the Moon.

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:18.760
Supreme Spirit, Earth, Sky, Heaven and Omkāra

00:03:18.880 --> 00:03:22.560
Saying Ganas first letter (G) at the beginning,

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:26.400
The first letter of the alphabet (A) next.

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:29.680
And the nasal sound (M) after that.

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:34.280
The crescent resounding, completed with the Om.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:38.480
This is the true form of Your mantra.

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:41.560
'G’ is the first form.

00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:44.800
'A' is the middle form.

00:03:44.880 --> 00:03:48.200
And 'M' is the last form

00:03:48.320 --> 00:03:51.360
Bindu (dot) is the finishing form on top

00:03:51.480 --> 00:03:53.960
With the sounds united

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:56.160
according to Sandhi.

00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:59.360
In this manner, is the knowledge of Shri Ganesha.

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:01.720
The seer is sage Ganaka.

00:04:01.800 --> 00:04:04.920
The metre is a mixed Gāyatrī.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.560
The presiding Deity is Shri Ganapati.

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:12.440
'Om Gam', obeisance to the Lord of the Ganas.

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:15.640
We have the knowledge of the One-Tusked God.

00:04:15.720 --> 00:04:19.160
We meditate on the Lord with a Curved Trunk,

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:22.680
May the Ivoried God inspire and stimulate us.

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:25.960
One-tusked and four-handed

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:28.840
Wielder of the noose and elephant goad.

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:31.200
Holding a broken tusk and all blessings in the hands

00:04:31.320 --> 00:04:35.160
Having a mouse as an emblem.

00:04:35.240 --> 00:04:37.760
Red-coloured, with a big belly,

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:39.960
Ears like winnowing fans

00:04:40.080 --> 00:04:42.400
Wearing red chothes

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:45.560
With fragrant red sandalwood paste anointing the body.

00:04:45.640 --> 00:04:48.840
Auspiciously worshipped with red flowers.

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:51.200
The God who is Compassionate to devotees,

00:04:51.320 --> 00:04:55.040
The Imperishable Origin of the world,

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:58.520
And becoming manifest at the beginning of creation.

00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:01.920
Being beyond the Ādi Shakti and the Supreme Spirit.

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:05.040
Whoever meditates in this way constantly,

00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:08.520
That Yogi becomes the most excellent of Yogis.

00:05:08.640 --> 00:05:11.120
We bow to the Lord of Assemblies

00:05:11.240 --> 00:05:13.520
and Chief of Ganas

00:05:13.640 --> 00:05:16.360
Prostrations to the Leader of Lord Shiva’s hordes,

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:19.840
Let there be obeisance to the Big-bellied,

00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:21.920
One-toothed,

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:23.960
Destroyer of Obstacles,

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:26.080
the Son of Lord Shiva

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:31.720
To the Embodiment of the Giver of prosperity and boons, Salutations.

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:37.640
Sakshat Shri Adi Shakti Mataji

00:05:37.640 --> 00:05:45.400
Shri Nirmala Devi Namoh Namah.

